          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;[Verse 1] &lt;br /&gt;
My life is a movie and everyone&#039;s watching. &lt;br /&gt;
So let&#039;s get to the good part and past all the nonsense. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[Pre-Chorus] &lt;br /&gt;
Sometimes it&#039;s hard to do the right thing. &lt;br /&gt;
When the pressure&#039;s coming down like lightning. &lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s like they want me to be perfect. &lt;br /&gt;
When they don&#039;t even know that I&#039;m hurting. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[Chorus] &lt;br /&gt;
