You act like you know me, but you never will. &lt;br /&gt;
But that&#039;s one thing that I know for sure. &lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;ll show you. I&#039;ll show you. &lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;ll show you. I&#039;ll show you. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[Verse 2] &lt;br /&gt;
